{"tid":467884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"只顧聊天　揸的士硬撼拖車　 危駕害死女友　司機囚16月","createTime":"2017-11-14T01:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T05:26:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0679ab19b2c194f6b387c9b5000172469e036b76","tid":467884,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:50:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171114/20213728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171114%2F20213728&d=nUiqQaqfiwN1mylpE5SRoAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=8532b97f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171114%2F20213728&h=af7a6586\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171114/20213728</a><br />\n<br />\n只顧聊天　揸的士硬撼拖車　<br />\n危駕害死女友　司機囚16月<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171114/large/a1001a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171114%2Flarge%2Fa1001a.gif&h=6817ddac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肇事的士車頭嚴重損毀。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年10月颱風海馬除下後，一名油站女職員於凌晨登上男朋友所駕的士趕往上班，兩人言談甚歡，男友完全不察覺前方有壞車，硬撼拖車車尾。女友頭部重創，送院11天後不治。案發後仍因不守交通標誌及超速被定罪的男友，昨在區域法院承認一項危險駕駛導致他人死亡罪，辯方指他自以為駕駛技術了得才釀禍。法官斥被告駕駛態度惡劣，判入獄16個月，停牌5年。<br />\n<br />\n記者：歐陽聯發<br />\n<br />\n控方透露，被告林詠明（52歲）有3次不小心駕駛及10次超速紀錄。辯方求情指，被告駕駛紀錄雖然不佳，但仍不算最差，過往沒有釀成大意外；被告承認與死者黃金福（31歲）只顧聊天，他駕駛的士十多年，自以為駕駛技術好，沒有留意路況，的士當時稍稍超速10公里，不算嚴重；意外前一刻被告察覺前方有拖車，已即時急轉右方閃避，但左邊車頭仍撞上拖車車尾；被告是死者的男朋友，事件留下很大創傷，感內疚及後悔。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官斥駕駛態度惡劣<br />\n<br />\n法官於判刑時直言，被告的駕駛態度惡劣，案發大埔公路段是一條直路，被告的視線沒有受阻，兩車相撞前被告有足足5秒時間可以切線，他卻只顧與女友聊天；當時颱風訊號剛除下，路面仍然濕滑，被告沒有顧及路況而超速。另一方面，被告過往有多次駕駛定罪紀錄，案發後兩個月仍因不遵照交通標誌駕駛被罰，今年6月又再超速，法官斥被告駕駛態度惡劣。<br />\n<br />\n意外發生於去年10月22日凌晨，被告所駕的士沿大埔公路前行，以時速約90公里行駛，超出80公里時速限制。事發前，一輛旅遊巴因故障停在大埔公路慢線，一輛拖車到場準備將車拖走，兩車都亮着死火燈提醒其他車輛。未料被告駕駛的士硬撼拖車右車尾，死者頭骨爆裂腦漿溢出。被告警誡下承認一邊與死者聊天一邊駕車，沒有留意前方；他又稱感覺光線昏暗，無法看到前車死火燈，當他發現時為時已晚，未能及時扭軚避免意外。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC504/17<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171114/large/a1001b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171114%2Flarge%2Fa1001b.gif&h=e698da4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女死者黃金福送院11天後不治。"},{"pid":"860f7f2cc7889672038e86ecdcd77abffc4b2146","tid":467884,"uid":18283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T02:29:38.000Z","msg":"的士狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd6c302c41f1dc46539a6209aaaa619fa6badaf","tid":467884,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T02:31:10.000Z","msg":"香港殺人方法最好都係咁。"},{"pid":"1dec04319b28822132279074c18ded7d12ae6103","tid":467884,"uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T02:31:57.000Z","msg":"DC9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600e92b82e7f9e37cb22fe428da28717a7529345","tid":467884,"uid":10094,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T02:32:56.000Z","msg":"52歲 31歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要叫黃金福 又拉個大陸女人落黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd08c3fb75772730e76b0d126d8bd1b301c090a7","tid":467884,"uid":127716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T02:33:35.000Z","msg":"垃圾的士狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f266e3151b79ea6724fd1c4cff835f2cff6627","tid":467884,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T02:33:50.000Z","msg":"黃金福仁商場"},{"pid":"01ad5cba0cdf6fe9bc1e222bf501a859b03027f4","tid":467884,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T02:35:03.000Z","msg":"撞死人都係坐16個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030dc0f13a538692876f7bbd092ca0759b7d93af","tid":467884,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T02:38:18.000Z","msg":"九成係支那女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60adfb7c8711b503cb850f06627c481290f6535","tid":467884,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T02:39:33.000Z","msg":"的士狗廢老累死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a3d7933be5511697677f6e3d40247dac0980e6","tid":467884,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T02:42:43.000Z","msg":"交通意外死人成日判咁輕"},{"pid":"d09be5d85085ecae1559eea422e98b7bf954c26a","tid":467884,"uid":61443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T04:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>52歲 31歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要叫黃金福 又拉個大陸女人落黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢鋪雙贏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c4739216b540a48f93e28e4629f8edba267701","tid":467884,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T04:43:03.000Z","msg":"一路睇以為男女個名掉轉咗"},{"pid":"ebfb797f61e987ef07546a066118db3a763510c5","tid":467884,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:26:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港殺人方法最好都係咁。</blockquote><br />\n成本最低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}